worried of them if they don't know R6, for example. They don't know S4, for example. I'm not

00:18:50.719 --> 00:18:58.319
worried. They will learn this quickly. So definitely not worried from that perspective, but what you

00:18:58.319 --> 00:19:04.319
just said is something that we're trying to conduct as well. There is a couple of steps that I usually

00:19:04.319 --> 00:19:12.719
do. I do want to know, I'm more concerned about their base R techniques, and then it increases.

